quran[61]{c,v,t}:
  37,22,"Gather those who were unjust/oppressive and their spouses , and what they were worshipping"
  37,23,"From other than God, so guide them to the Hell`s road/way"
  37,24,"And stop/suspend them , that they are questioned"
  37,25,"And what (is it) for you, you do not give victory/aid"
  37,26,But they are the day/today submitting/surrendering
  37,27,"And some of them approached/came on (to) some, they ask/question each other"
  37,28,"They said: \"That you were coming to us from the right (side)"
  37,29,"They said: \"But you were not being believing"
  37,30,"And (there) was not from power/control for us over you, but you were a tyrannizing/arrogant nation"
  37,31,"So became deserved on us our Lord`s word/saying , that we (are) tasting/experiencing"
  37,32,"So we misguided/lured you , that we were misguiding"
  37,33,So then they are (on) that day in the torture sharing
  37,34,"We, like that, We make/do with the criminals/sinners"
  37,35,"That they truly were if (it) was said to them: \"No God except god\" they be arrogant"
  37,36,"And they say: \"Are we to leave our gods to a mad/insane poet"
  37,37,But He came with the truth and he confirmed the messengers
  37,38,"That you are tasting/experiencing the torture, the painful"
  37,39,And you are not being reimbursed except (for) what you were making/doing/working
  37,40,"Except God`s worshippers/slaves , the faithful/loyal"
  37,41,"Those, for them (is) a known provision"
  37,42,"Fruits, and they are honoured"
  37,43,In the blessed/comfort and ease treed gardens/paradises
  37,44,On beds/sofas facing each other
  37,45,Being circled/walked around on them with a cup/container to drink from/wine from goodness
  37,46,White (a) delight/pleasure to the drinking
  37,47,"Destruction/intoxication (is) not in it, nor they be drunk/made to loose their minds/drained/exhausted from it"
  37,48,And at them the eye`s/eyelid`s confining/limiting/restricting big beautiful eyes
  37,49,As though they are (F) protected/covered whites/eggs
  37,50,"So some of them approached/came on (to) some, they ask/question each other"
  37,51,"A speaker from them said: \"That I, (there) was for me (a) companion"
  37,52,"He says: \"You are (E) from the confirming/charity givers"
  37,53,"Is (it that) if we died, and we were dust and bones are we indebted (E)"
  37,54,"He said: \"Are you knowing/seeing/looking"
  37,55,"So he looked/saw, so he saw him in the Hell`s middle"
  37,56,"He said: \"By God if you were about to to make me fall/ruin (E)"
  37,57,And where it not for my Lord`s blessing/goodness I would have been from the made present/attending
  37,58,So are we not with dying
  37,59,"Except our death/lifelessness the first/beginning, and we are not with being tortured"
  37,60,That this it is (E) the winning/success the great
  37,61,"Similar/equal/alike to this, so the makers/doers/workers, should make/do/work"
  37,62,Is that a better place of descent or the deadly food`s tree
  37,63,That We made/put it (as) a test/charm to the unjust/oppressive
  37,64,That it is a tree it emerges in the Hell`s source/root
  37,65,Its first fruit of the season as though it (is) the devils` heads/tops
  37,66,"So then they are eating exaggerated/gluttons from it, so they are filling from it the bellies/insides"
  37,67,Then for them on it (is) a mixture/heat (E) from hot/cold water/red hot coal
  37,68,Then that their return (is) to (E) the Hell
  37,69,That they truly found their fathers misguided
  37,70,So they are on their tracks/marks/signs rushing disturbedly
  37,71,And most of the first/beginners had been (E) misguided before them
  37,72,And We had (E) sent in (between) them warners/givers of notice
  37,73,So look/see/wonder about how was the warned`s/given notice`s end/turn (result)
  37,74,"Except God`s worshippers/slaves , the faithful/loyal/devoted"
  37,75,"And Noah had called/cried (to) Us, so blessed/praised (E) (are) the answerers/repliers"
  37,76,"And We saved/rescued him and his family/relation from the grief, hardship and suffering the great"
  37,77,"And We made/put his descendants, they are the remaining"
  37,78,And We left on him in the lasts
  37,79,Peace/security on Noah in the creations are together/(universes)
  37,80,"We (E) like that, We reimburse the good doers"
  37,81,"That he truly is from Our worshippers/slaves , the believers"
  37,82,Then We drowned/sunk the others/lasts